name: Protonono! (Krummhorn Games)
description:
As a proton inside a particle collider, your only goal is to smash into another proton at breakneck speed, but with black holes lurking at every turn, your mission won't be easy!

Gain speed by flying past black holes, but be careful not to get too close or your journey will end prematurely. All the while, entropy is out to get you, so don't wait too long.

Can you survive the journey long enough to make the ultimate collision?
